title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 3 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 3 2022
description:
White House commands Big Tech to censor enemies, liberal artists fall in line. Buck says, "There's actual collusion going on between this White House and Big Tech." Why the Democrats can't stand Tulsi Gabbard. Credit to all the kids standing up to mask insanity across the country. This is what teen rebellion should be about, Clay cheers. C&B talk to Eric Flannery, D.C. bar owner defying mandates because he says he just knows he's right: His business and others should be open.
